snippet.title: Call of Duty: WWII Gameplay Interview | E3 2017
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/call-of-duty-wwii-ps4/

The iconic FPS series returns to its roots with explosive, boots-on-the-ground gameplay in Call of Duty: WWII. We talk with the team behind the game live from E3 2017, exploring the heart-pounding campaign and what awaits us in a new multiplayer suite.
